Ovid also considers love as a science or art that must be learned. In the Ars amatoria Ovid poses as the teacher of love. At other times love is a sort of warfare. Love is the leader and the lover is a soldier* In Ovid's works love is also treated as a disease and Ovid becomes the doctor of love in the Remedia armaris⁴
